https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r8MsiouTKfjZOphznu9V2gGvSjG.jpg Cover-up '62 is based on the final days and tragic death of screen legend Marilyn Monroe. In an attempt to calm her down after a sudden argument, RFK and Dr. Greenson administer a fatal dose of Nembutal. Instead of calling the authorities with the help of Peter Lawford and the Secret Service her death is covered up as a suicide. Cover-Up '62
